---
import BaseLayout from "../../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const appUrl = "/apps/preset-mutator/ui/";
const gumroadUrl = "https://kreativ.gumroad.com/l/preset-mutator-pro";
const softwareSchema = {
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "SoftwareApplication",
  name: "Preset Mutator",
  applicationCategory: "MultimediaApplication",
  operatingSystem: "Web browser",
  description: "Preset Mutator creates Vital preset starting points from scratch ideas, existing Vital presets, or short audio sources. Serum 2 and Pigments 7 support are planned.",
  url: "https://kreativsound.com/tools/preset-mutator/",
  image: "https://kreativsound.com/apps/preset-mutator/ui/preset-mutator-mark.svg",
  offers: {
    "@type": "Offer",
    url: gumroadUrl,
    price: "19",
    priceCurrency: "USD",
    availability: "https://schema.org/InStock"
  },
  creator: {
    "@type": "Person",
    name: "Andrei Olaru"
  }
};
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Preset Mutator | Kreativ Sound"
  description="Preset Mutator is a browser-based preset generation tool for Vital, with From Scratch, Mutate Preset, and Audio to Preset workflows."
  canonical="https://kreativsound.com/tools/preset-mutator/"
  activeNav="tools"
  ogImage="https://kreativsound.com/apps/preset-mutator/ui/preset-mutator-mark.svg"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(softwareSchema)} />
  <article class="card page-main product-page product-page-modern tools-page preset-mutator-sales-page">
    <section class="product-hero preset-mutator-sales-hero">
      <div class="product-hero-copy">
        <p class="product-kicker">Browser tool</p>
        <h1 class="page-title">Preset Mutator</h1>
        <p class="page-lead">Create Vital preset starts from scratch, from one preset, or from one short audio source.</p>
        <p class="product-summary">Preset Mutator is a local-first browser tool for fast sound-design sketching. It is built for usable starting points, not final automated mix-ready magic.</p>
        <div class="product-specs-inline" aria-label="Preset Mutator summary">
          <div class="product-spec-inline">
            <span class="product-spec-label">Live now</span>
            <span class="product-spec-value">Vital export</span>
          </div>
          <div class="product-spec-inline">
            <span class="product-spec-label">Pro price</span>
            <span class="product-spec-value">$19 one-time</span>
          </div>
          <div class="product-spec-inline">
            <span class="product-spec-label">Planned next</span>
            <span class="product-spec-value">Serum 2 + Pigments 7</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="product-trust-line">Runs locally in your browser. No AI preset generation. No uploads or stored presets/audio.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="product-hero-media preset-mutator-sales-card">
        <div class="preset-mutator-mark-frame">
          <img src="/apps/preset-mutator/ui/preset-mutator-mark.svg" width="220" height="220" alt="Preset Mutator mark" />
        </div>
        <div class="product-media-actions">
          <a class="button primary" href={appUrl}>
            <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            Open Free Version
          </a>
          <a class="button secondary" href={gumroadUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-lock" aria-hidden="true"></i>
            Unlock Pro
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="product-value-line">Free mode generates 3 Vital starts. Pro unlocks 32-preset packs and ZIP export.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="product-proof-strip preset-mutator-proof" aria-label="Preset Mutator trust points">
      <article>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-laptop-code" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <p>Processing happens in the browser, so source material does not need to be uploaded.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-ban" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <p>No AI generation: presets are built from local rules and curated seed data.</p>
      </article>
      <article>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-key" aria-hidden="true"></i>
        <p>Purchase-code unlock keeps the first release simple while the workflow is still young.</p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="product-story-grid preset-mutator-mode-grid">
      <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern product-panel-accent">
        <p class="product-section-kicker">Default</p>
        <h2>From Scratch</h2>
        <p>Start with intent, mood, register, and shape controls. Best when you want a quick playable idea without feeding the app a source file.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern">
        <p class="product-section-kicker">Preset source</p>
        <h2>Mutate Preset</h2>
        <p>Load one `.vital` preset and create related variations while keeping the original identity close enough to refine in Vital.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern">
        <p class="product-section-kicker">Audio source</p>
        <h2>Audio to Preset</h2>
        <p>Analyze one short sound locally and turn it into Vital preset directions. Best for simple tones, textures, drones, and focused one-shots.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="product-panel product-panel-modern product-panel-accent">
        <p class="product-section-kicker">Roadmap</p>
        <h2>Vital first, then expansion</h2>
        <p>Vital is the stable first target. Serum 2 and Pigments 7 should come after the core workflows are proven and easier to support.</p>
      </article>
    </section>

    <section class="preset-mutator-compare" aria-labelledby="preset-mutator-compare-title">
      <div>
        <p class="product-section-kicker">Free vs Pro</p>
        <h2 id="preset-mutator-compare-title">Keep the free version useful, make Pro about volume and export speed.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="preset-mutator-compare-grid">
        <article>
          <h3>Free</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>3 Vital preset starts per workflow.</li>
            <li>Manual download of generated presets.</li>
            <li>Local browser processing and no account requirement.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
        <article>
          <h3>Pro</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>32-preset pack generation.</li>
            <li>ZIP export for faster preset collection building.</li>
            <li>One-time purchase-code unlock for this browser.</li>
          </ul>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="product-cta-strip">
      <div class="product-cta-copy">
        <p class="product-section-kicker">Release focus</p>
        <p class="product-cta-line">The strongest next step is to finish the Vital workflow, prove that people want it, then add Serum 2 and Pigments 7 support without renaming the product again.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="product-actions">
        <a class="button primary" href={appUrl}>
          <i class="fa-solid fa-wand-magic-sparkles" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          Open Preset Mutator
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
